(http://junit-addons.sourceforge.net). The JUnit-Addons code includes no modifications.
The use of JUnit-Addons in both source and binary code form contained here
is subject to the terms and conditions of the Apache Software License.
The binary code is located in the lib directory in the file junit-addons-1.4.jar.

